<h1>Overview</h1>
<h2>What is Cadmium?</h2>
<p>Cadmium is a static content distribution system backed by <a href="http://www.github.com">GitHub</a> repositories.  It provides the following features:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Dynamic Content Update</li>
  <li>Content Cloning</li>
  <li>Audit Service</li>
  <li>Search Service</li>
  <li>Email This Page</li>
  <li>SSH Required Pages</li>
  <li>Redirect Service</li>
  <li>Dynamic Copyright updating</li>
  <li>pdf-concatenation service</li>
  <li>JBOSS War Deployer</li>
  <li>Scheduler Service</li>
  <li>Cluster Syncronization</li>
  <li>Lifecycle notifications</li>
  <li>Dynamic Configuration Framework</li>
  <li>Database framework</li>
  <li>Basic Auth framework</li>
  <li>Automatic Module Discovery</li>
  <li>REST api framework</li>
  <li>Captcha Integration</li>
</ul>














